content: I have been messaging here since yesterday. I just received a private message, not sure why private, that apparently the system is not working for people who want to volunteer from abroad. Is that correct? There is no solution?
It is very strange because I did this from here (France) in the last Biden election.
We use 2 different platforms that we didn't use in 2020 actually but it should work.
What error message does it say.
